jedde ikke f\u00f8r. I tillegg opplever vi at det slakkes p\u00e5 vintervedlikeholdet. N\u00e5r vi n\u00e5 vurderer E6, har det med sikkerheten v\u00e5r \u00e5 gj\u00f8re. Sj\u00e5f\u00f8rene opplever nesten daglig nesten-ulykker."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "ccef1e45c680d99f006430a1842dc1d7dabef7fbe536ad2cf44316fedb95cafb"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-12-13T09:55:40.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Yrkessj\u00e5f\u00f8rene kj\u00f8rer gjennom \u00d8sterdalen med hjertet i halsen. N\u00e5 vurderer de \u00e5 flytte trailertrafikken til Gudbrandsdalen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1235336.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/OEsterdalen_tungtransport_02"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ff7737745fa69a914131c6fe473403e368ffa632.jpg?5979dbf2"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Trailersj\u00e5f\u00f8rer vil endre rute -adressa.no", "Frykter for sikkerheten", "Vil ha ny riksvei 3", "- Livsfarlig i \u00d8sterdalen"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "ff7737745fa69a914131c6fe473403e368ffa632"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "automotive"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["ulykke skjer", "riksvei", "vedlikehold", "endre rute", "sj\u00e5f\u00f8ren", "dag", "transport", "kj\u00f8re", "veien"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["myhrvold", "leiv sand transport og karl \u00f8yvind lomundal", "b\u00f8rstad", "heimdal", "t\u00f8mmermo", "gudbrandsdalen", 